ra / [[Michael Sch\u00f8nwandt]]\n*Historic Archive &ndash; [[Berlioz]], [[Les troyens|Les Troyens]], Covent Garden Opera / [[Rafael Kubel\u00edk]]\n*Opera &ndash; [[Puccini]], [[Madama Butterfly]], [[Accademia Nazionale di Santa Cecilia]] / [[Antonio Pappano]], [[Angela Gheorghiu]] (sop)\n*Orchestral &ndash; [[Tchaikovsky]], [[Manfred Symphony]] & The Vayevoda, [[Royal Liverpool Philharmonic]] / [[Vasily Petrenko]]\n*Editors Choice : Beethoven: Diabelli Variations & Bach: Partita No. 4 \u2013 Stephen Kovacevich (piano)\n\n===2008===\n*Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Hilary Hahn]]\n*Lifetime Achievement &ndash; [[Andr\u00e9 Previn]]\n*Young Artist of the Year &ndash; [[Maxim Rysanov]]\n*Special Achievement &ndash; [[Peter Moores (businessman)|Sir Peter Moores]]\n*Label of the Year &ndash; [[Hyperion Records|Hyperion]]\n*The Gold Disc &ndash; [[Camille Saint-Sa\u00ebns|Saint-Sa\u00ebns]]: Piano Concertos \u2013 [[Stephen Hough]]\n*Classic FM Award for Audience Innovation &ndash; [[Tasmin Little]]\n*Baroque Instrumental &ndash; ''[[Brandenburg concertos]]'' European Brandenburg Ensemble / [[Trevor Pinnock]] (Avie)\n*Chamber &ndash; [[Brahms]] and [[Robert Schumann|Schumann]], ''Piano quintets'', [[Leif Ove Andsnes]], Artemis Quartet (Virgin Classics)\n*Concerto &ndash; [[Elgar]], ''[[Violin Concerto (Elgar)|Violin Concerto]]'', [[James Ehnes]], [[Philharmonia Orchestra]] / [[Andrew Davis (conductor)|Sir Andrew Davis]] (Onyx)\n*DVD &ndash; [[Mozart]], ''[[Le nozze di Figaro]]'' Soloists, The Royal Opera / [[Antonio Pappano]] (Opus Arte)\n*Historic Archive &ndash; [[Vaughan Williams]], [[Symphony No. 5 (Vaughan Williams)|Symphony No 5]] [[London Philharmonic Orchestra]] / [[Vaughan Williams]] (Somm)\n*Opera &ndash; [[Jan\u00e1\u010dek]], [[The Excursions of Mr. Brou\u010dek to the Moon and to the 15th Century|The Excursions of Mr Broucek]] [[BBC Symphony Orchestra]] / [[Jir\u00ed Belohl\u00e1vek]] ([[Deutsche Grammophon]])\n*Recital &ndash; ''Maria'', [[Cecilia Bartoli]], 