le]]\n*Baroque Instrumental &ndash; ''[[Brandenburg concertos]]'' European Brandenburg Ensemble / [[Trevor Pinnock]] (Avie)\n*Chamber &ndash; [[Brahms]] and [[Robert Schumann|Schumann]], ''Piano quintets'', [[Leif Ove Andsnes]], Artemis Quartet (Virgin Classics)\n*Concerto &ndash; [[Elgar]], ''[[Violin Concerto (Elgar)|Violin Concerto]]'', [[James Ehnes]], [[Philharmonia Orchestra]] / [[Andrew Davis (conductor)|Sir Andrew Davis]] (Onyx)\n*DVD &ndash; [[Mozart]], ''[[Le nozze di Figaro]]'' Soloists, The Royal Opera / [[Antonio Pappano]] (Opus Arte)\n*Historic Archive &ndash; [[Vaughan Williams]], [[Symphony No. 5 (Vaughan Williams)|Symphony No 5]] [[London Philharmonic Orchestra]] / [[Vaughan Williams]] (Somm)\n*Opera &ndash; [[Jan\u00e1\u010dek]], [[The Excursions of Mr. Brou\u010dek to the Moon and to the 15th Century|The Excursions of Mr Broucek]] [[BBC Symphony Orchestra]] / [[Jir\u00ed Belohl\u00e1vek]] ([[Deutsche Grammophon]])\n*Recital &ndash; ''Maria'', [[Cecilia Bartoli]], [[Orchestra La Scintilla]] / [[\u00c1d\u00e1m Fischer]] (Decca)\n*Instrumental (Record of the Year) &ndash; [[Beethoven]], ''Piano Sonatas, Vol 4'' [[Paul Lewis (pianist)|Paul Lewis]] ([[Harmonia Mundi]])\n*Baroque Vocal &ndash; [[Monteverdi]], ''[[L'Orfeo]]'', [[La Venexiana]] / [[Claudio Cavina]] (Glossa)\n*Choral &ndash; [[Haydn]], ''[[The Creation (Haydn)|The Creation]]'', Soloists, Gabrieli Consort and Players / [[Paul McCreesh]] ([[Archiv Produktion]])\n*Contemporary &ndash; [[Jonathan Harvey (composer)|Jonathan Harvey]], Body Mandala, Anu Komsi, [[BBC Scottish Symphony Orchestra]] / [[Ilan Volkov]] (NMC)\n*Early Music &ndash; [[Nicholas Ludford]], Missa Benedicta, Choir of New College, Oxford / Edward Higginbottom (K617)\n*Historic Reissue \u2013 [[Sibelius]], ''Songs'', [[Kim Borg]], [[Erik Werba]] ([[Deutsche Grammophon]])\n*Orchestral &ndash; [[Myaskovsky]], ''Symphonies'', USSR State & Russian Federation Symphony Orchestras / [[Evgeny Svetlanov]] (Warner Classics)\n*Solo vocal 