ary Democratic debate |author=Kendall Karson |website=ABC News |date=January 22, 2020 |access-date=January 22, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! [[2020 Democratic Party presidential debates#Ninth debate (February 19, 2020)|9]]\n| February 19, 2020\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |9\u201311&nbsp;p.m.<ref name=\"NVNBC \"/>\n| ~33.16 million<br />(19.66m live TV; 13.5m streaming)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/democratic-debate-criminal-minds-tv-ratings-wednesday-feb-19-2020-1280119 |title=TV Ratings: Ninth Democratic Debate Breaks Viewer Record for Party |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |author=Rick Porter |date=February 20, 2020 |access-date=February 20, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Democratic Debate Snags Record 20 Million Viewers: NBC |url=https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/02/20/arts/20reuters-usa-election-debate-ratings.html |work=[[Reuters]] |date=February 20, 2020 |access-date=February 20, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Bloomberg's addition to the Democratic debate stage leads to record viewership |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/20/bloombergs-addition-to-democratic-debate-stage-leads-to-record-viewership.html |author=Yelena Dzhanova |work=[[CNBC]] |date=February 20, 2020 |access-date=February 20, 2020}}</ref>\n| Le Th\u00e9\u00e2tre des Arts, <br />[[Paris Las Vegas]],<br />[[Paradise, Nevada]]<ref name=\"NVNBC \"/>\n|[[NBC News]]<br />[[MSNBC]]<br />[[Telemundo]]<br />''[[The Nevada Independent]]''\n| Vanessa Hauc<br />[[Lester Holt]]<br />[[Hallie Jackson]]<br />[[Jon Ralston]]<br />[[Chuck Todd]]<ref name=\"NVNBC\">{{cite web |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2020-election/nbc-news-msnbc-announce-5-moderators-democratic-debate-las-vegas-n1130711 |title=NBC News, MSNBC announce 5 moderators for Democratic debate in Las Vegas |website=NBC News |last1=Smith |first1=Allan |language=en |date=February 6, 2020 |access-date=2020-02-05}}</ref>\n|-\n! [[2020 Democratic Party presidential debates#Tenth debate (February 25, 2020)|10]